{"article_id":"LxKhGvI0x3IxPi6Y","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Washington ( CNN )","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"A former Trump campaign foreign policy adviser has pleaded guilty to making a false statement to the FBI","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"after he lied about his interactions with foreign officials close to the Russian government","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"-- the campaign 's clearest connection so far to Russia 's efforts","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"to meddle in the 2016 election .","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"In court records","depth":10},{"id":6,"text":"unsealed on Monday ,","depth":10},{"id":7,"text":"the FBI said","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"George Papadopoulos `` falsely described his interactions with a certain foreign contact","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"who discussed 'dirt '","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"related to emails ''","depth":11},{"id":11,"text":"concerning Democratic presidential candidate Hillary Clinton .","depth":11},{"id":12,"text":"Records also describe an email between Trump campaign officials","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"suggesting","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"they were considering acting on Russian invitations","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"to go to Russia .","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"In addition , former Trump campaign chairman Paul Manafort and former Trump campaign official Rick Gates surrendered Monday to Justice Department special counsel Robert Mueller .","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"The charges against top officials from Trump 's campaign signals a dramatic new phase of Mueller 's wide-ranging investigation into possible collusion between the Russian government and members of Trump 's team as well as potential obstruction of justice and financial crimes .","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"Papadopoulos ' guilty plea brings the Mueller probe into actions","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"that occurred during the 2016 campaign .","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"The charges against Manafort and Gates are unrelated to the Trump campaign ,","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"though it 's possible Mueller could add additional charges .","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"Gates , 45 , is a longtime business associate of Manafort , 68 .","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"The pair worked together since the mid-2000s ,","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"and Gates served as Manafort 's deputy on the campaign .","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"The two were indicted under seal on Friday ,","depth":6},{"id":26,"text":"a source with direct knowledge of the matter said .","depth":6},{"id":27,"text":"President Donald Trump distanced himself from Manafort on Monday morning ,","depth":5},{"id":28,"text":"asking","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"why Clinton was n't being investigated .","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"`` Sorry ,","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"but this is years ago ,","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"before Paul Manafort was part of the Trump campaign .","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"But why are n't Crooked Hillary & the Dems the focus ? ? ? ? ? ''","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"He soon added :","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"`` Also , there is NO COLLUSION ! ''","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"Sorry ,","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"but this is years ago ,","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"before Paul Manafort was part of the Trump campaign .","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"But why are n't Crooked Hillary & the Dems the focus ? ? ? ? ?","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"October 30 , 2017 ....","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"Also , there is NO COLLUSION !","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"October 30 , 2017","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"Campaign official suggested","depth":4},{"id":48,"text":"'low level ' staff should go to Russia","depth":4},{"id":49,"text":"Papadopoulos lied to FBI agents `` about the timing , extent and nature of his relationships and interactions with certain foreign nationals","depth":6},{"id":50,"text":"whom he understood to have close connections with senior Russian government officials , ''","depth":6},{"id":51,"text":"according to the complaint .","depth":5},{"id":52,"text":"Mueller signed a 14-page statement","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"regarding Papadopoulos ' offense ,","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"which lays out of the facts of the case .","depth":6},{"id":55,"text":"In May , Papadopoulos sent an email to a `` high-ranking campaign official '' with the subject line `` Request from Russia","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"to meet Mr . Trump . ''","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"The email said","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"Russian officials were eager to meet with the candidate","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"and had been reaching out .","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"In a footnote , the FBI statement notes","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"that the email","depth":13},{"id":62,"text":"suggesting a Russia visit","depth":13},{"id":63,"text":"was forwarded from one campaign official to another .","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"`` We need someone","depth":13},{"id":65,"text":"to communicate","depth":14},{"id":66,"text":"that DT is not doing these trips .","depth":14},{"id":67,"text":"It should be someone low level in the campaign","depth":13},{"id":68,"text":"so as not to send any signal , ''","depth":13},{"id":69,"text":"the email read .","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"The FBI statement does not explain","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"to whom the campaign officials were concerned about sending signals .","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"In the affidavit","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"connected to the case ,","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"there is a reference to a July 2016 email","depth":12},{"id":75,"text":"Papadopoulos sent to a foreign contact","depth":12},{"id":76,"text":"regarding setting up a meeting with what appears to be Manafort","depth":12},{"id":77,"text":"( described in the email as his `` national chairman '' ) .","depth":12},{"id":78,"text":"Papadopoulos writes","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"the meeting has been `` approved from our side . ''","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"Mueller 's statement also says","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"that Papadopoulos met in March 2016 with a Russian woman","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"-- introduced to him as a relative of Russian President Vladimir Putin ,","depth":12},{"id":83,"text":"though she was not --","depth":12},{"id":84,"text":"and he sought to use her connections","depth":11},{"id":85,"text":"to arrange a meeting between the campaign and Russian government officials .","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"The statement also says","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"that Papadopoulos falsely claimed","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"he met with an overseas professor","depth":12},{"id":89,"text":"before joining the Trump campaign","depth":12},{"id":90,"text":"about `` the Russians possessing 'dirt ' on then-candidate Hillary Clinton in the form of 'thousands of emails . ' ''","depth":11},{"id":91,"text":"The professor only took interest in Papadopoulos","depth":10},{"id":92,"text":"because of his status on the campaign ,","depth":10},{"id":93,"text":"according to the statement .","depth":9},{"id":94,"text":"A former Trump campaign official said","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"Papadopoulos interacted with the campaign `` a significant amount '' during the 2016 election cycle .","depth":11},{"id":96,"text":"`` He was a foreign policy adviser , ''","depth":12},{"id":97,"text":"said the official ,","depth":13},{"id":98,"text":"who described Papadopoulos as an adviser","depth":14},{"id":99,"text":"who was in contact with the campaign staff via email and not a familiar face around Trump Tower .","depth":14},{"id":100,"text":"The official said","depth":12},{"id":101,"text":"Papadopoulos exchanged emails `` constantly '' on foreign policy matters with the Trump team during the campaign .","depth":12},{"id":102,"text":"Another former senior campaign adviser said of Papadopoulos :","depth":10},{"id":103,"text":"`` He was a zero .","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"A non-event . ''","depth":11},{"id":105,"text":"When asked about Papadopoulos ' role in the campaign ,","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"White House press secretary Sarah Sanders told reporters","depth":11},{"id":107,"text":"his role was `` extremely limited ''","depth":12},{"id":108,"text":"and called it a `` volunteer position . ''","depth":12},{"id":109,"text":"Sanders said","depth":13},{"id":110,"text":"the fact","depth":15},{"id":111,"text":"that Papadopoulos did not tell the truth","depth":15},{"id":112,"text":"`` has nothing","depth":15},{"id":113,"text":"to do with the campaign ''","depth":15},{"id":114,"text":"and said","depth":13},{"id":115,"text":"he never acted in an official capacity .","depth":13},{"id":116,"text":"`` He reached out","depth":12},{"id":117,"text":"and nothing happened beyond that .","depth":12},{"id":118,"text":"That shows one , his level of importance in the campaign ,","depth":11},{"id":119,"text":"and two , shows what little role","depth":13},{"id":120,"text":"he had","depth":13},{"id":121,"text":"within coordinating anything officially for the campaign . ''","depth":12},{"id":122,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":6},{"id":123,"text":"Indictment against Manafort , Gates unsealed","depth":6},{"id":124,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":5},{"id":125,"text":"MUST WATCH Indictment against Manafort , Gates unsealed","depth":5},{"id":126,"text":"01:10","depth":5},{"id":127,"text":"The indictment against Manafort and Gates contains 12 counts :","depth":4},{"id":128,"text":"conspiracy against the United States , conspiracy","depth":5},{"id":129,"text":"to launder money , unregistered agent of a foreign principal , false and misleading US Foreign Agents Registration Act statements , false statements , and seven counts of failure","depth":6},{"id":130,"text":"to file reports of foreign bank and financial accounts .","depth":6},{"id":131,"text":"The two pleaded not guilty before US District Magistrate Judge Deborah Robinson on Monday afternoon .","depth":5},{"id":132,"text":"Other than stating their names ,","depth":6},{"id":133,"text":"neither man spoke .","depth":6},{"id":134,"text":"Gates was represented by a public defender .","depth":4},{"id":135,"text":"A federal judge ordered home confinement for Manafort and Gates","depth":5},{"id":136,"text":"and set bond at $ 10 million for Manafort and $ 5 million for Gates .","depth":5},{"id":137,"text":"The defendants will have to check in daily with law enforcement by phone ,","depth":5},{"id":138,"text":"and they will only be allowed to leave their homes","depth":6},{"id":139,"text":"to see their attorneys ,","depth":7},{"id":140,"text":"to appear at court or for medical and religious necessities .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":281,"left":262,"right":280,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":262,"left":187,"right":261,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":187,"left":167,"right":186,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":167,"left":156,"right":166,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":156,"left":0,"right":155,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":155,"left":144,"right":154,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":144,"left":1,"right":143,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":143,"left":2,"right":142,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":142,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":154,"left":150,"right":153,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":150,"left":146,"right":149,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":146,"left":145,"right":7,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":145,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":149,"left":8,"right":148,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":148,"left":9,"right":147,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":147,"left":10,"r